              <ul class="text-sm space-y-2 text-muted">
                <li>• LIDAR turbulence detection</li>
                <li>• Clear-air turbulence mitigation</li>
                <li>• Advanced weather forecasting</li>
                <li>• Real-time weather avoidance</li>
              </ul>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Regulatory Changes -->
        <div>
          <h3 class="font-serif text-2xl font-bold text-secondary mb-6">Regulatory Changes and Policy Updates</h3>

          <div class="space-y-6">
            <div class="bg-surface border border-gray-200 rounded-lg p-6">
              <h4 class="font-bold text-primary mb-4">Boeing 737 MAX Response</h4>
              <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-6">
                <div>
                  <h5 class="font-bold text-secondary mb-2">Certification Changes</h5>
                  <ul class="text-sm space-y-1 text-muted">
                    <li>• More stringent oversight of aircraft design</li>
                    <li>• Independent validation requirements</li>
                    <li>• Human factors considerations</li>
                    <li>• Pilot-automation interface standards</li>
                  </ul>
                </div>
                <div>
                  <h5 class="font-bold text-secondary mb-2">Training Mandates</h5>
                  <ul class="text-sm space-y-1 text-muted">
                    <li>• Enhanced simulator training requirements</li>
                    <li>• Automated system failure scenarios</li>
                    <li>• Manual flying skill maintenance</li>
                    <li>• Recurrent training protocols</li>
                  </ul>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>

            <div class="bg-surface border border-gray-200 rounded-lg p-6">
              <h4 class="font-bold text-primary mb-4">Other Significant Policy Updates</h4>
              <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-6">
                <div>
                  <h5 class="font-bold text-secondary mb-2">Pilot Qualifications</h5>
                  <p class="text-sm text-muted mb-2">
                    Colgan Air Flight 3407 (2009) led to FAA mandating increased minimum flight hours from 250 to 1,500 and stricter rest requirements <a href="#ref-374" class="citation">[374]</a>.
                  </p>
                </div>
                <div>
                  <h5 class="font-bold text-secondary mb-2">Conflict Zone Management</h5>
                  <p class="text-sm text-muted mb-2">
                    MH17 and PS752 shootdowns prompted enhanced risk assessment for flights near conflict zones and better military-civilian coordination.
                  </p>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>

